v></button><button class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-gray-200 card-hover shadow-card" style="animation:fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out 0.30000000000000004s both"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 group-hover:from-blue-50 transition-all duration-300"></div><div class="relative p-8 text-left h-full flex flex-col"><div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl text-purple-600 bg-purple-50 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-clipboard-list w-12 h-12"><rect width="8" height="4" x="8" y="2" rx="1" ry="1"></rect><path d="M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2"></path><path d="M12 11h4"></path><path d="M12 16h4"></path><path d="M8 11h.01"></path><path d="M8 16h.01"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Subir Proyecto</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-base leading-relaxed flex-grow">Petición de proyecto de climatización en Mallorca</p></div></button></div></div></div><div class="flex gap-4 justify-between items-center max-w-4xl mx-auto"><div class="flex-1 text-sm text-gray-400 italic">👆 Haz clic en un servicio para avanzar</div></div></div></main><section id="servicios" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6"><div class="text-center mb-12" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">Nuestros servicios</span><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">Todo lo que necesitas para tu climatización</h2><p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Servicio integral de aire acondicionado en Mallorca. Instalación, reparación y mantenimiento con garantía profesional.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6"><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-snowflake w-7 h-7 text-white"><line x1="2" x2="22" y1="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"></line><path d="m20 16-4-4 4-4"></path><path d="m4 8 4 4-4 4"></path><path d="m16 4-4 4-4-4"></path><path d="m8 20 4-4 4 4"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Instalación de aire acondicionado</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Instalación profesional de equipos de climatización con presupuesto cerrado. Desde splits hasta sistemas de conductos.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-teal-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-settings w-7 h-7 text-white"><path d="M12.22 2h-.44a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v.18a2 2 0 0 1-1 1.73l-.43.25a2 2 0 0 1-2 0l-.15-.08a2 2 0 0 0-2.73.73l-.22.38a2 2 0 0 0 .73 2.73l.15.1a2 2 0 0 1 1 1.72v.51a2 2 0 0 1-1 1.74l-.15.09a2 2 0 0 0-.73 2.73l.22.38a2 2 0 0 0 2.73.73l.15-.08a2 2 0 0 1 2 0l.43.25a2 2 0 0 1 1 1.73V20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h.44a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-.18a2 2 0 0 1 1-1.73l.43-.25a2 2 0 0 1 2 0l.15.08a2 2 0 0 0 2.73-.73l.22-.39a2 2 0 0 0-.73-2.73l-.15-.08a2 2 0 0 1-1-1.74v-.5a2 2 0 0 1 1-1.74l.15-.09a2 2 0 0 0 .73-2.73l-.22-.38a2 2 0 0 0-2.73-.73l-.15.08a2 2 0 0 1-2 0l-.43-.25a2 2 0 0 1-1-1.73V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Sustitución de equipos antiguos</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Cambia tu equipo antiguo por uno de última generación. Más eficiente, menos consumo y mejor confort.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-red-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-wrench w-7 h-7 text-white"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Reparación y averías</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Localizamos y solucionamos cualquier avería. Servicio de urgencia en 72h en temporada alta.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-green-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield w-7 h-7 text-white"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Mantenimiento preventivo</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Revisiones periódicas para alargar la vida útil de tu equipo y evitar averías costosas.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-indigo-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-building2 w-7 h-7 text-white"><path d="M6 22V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v18Z"></path><path d="M6 12H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2"></path><path d="M18 9h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2"></path><path d="M10 6h4"></path><path d="M10 10h4"></path><path d="M10 14h4"></path><path d="M10 18h4"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Proyectos personalizados</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Proyectos para hoteles, oficinas, locales comerciales y viviendas. Soluciones a medida.</p></div><div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) translateZ(0)"><div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thermometer-sun w-7 h-7 text-white"><path d="M12 9a4 4 0 0 0-2 7.5"></path><path d="M12 3v2"></path><path d="m6.6 18.4-1.4 1.4"></path><path d="M20 4v10.54a4 4 0 1 1-4 0V4a2 2 0 0 1 4 0Z"></path><path d="M4 13H2"></path><path d="M6.34 7.34 4.93 5.93"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Climatización eficiente</h3><p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Equipos de alta eficiencia energética (A+++) que reducen tu factura de la luz hasta un 40%.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="sobre-nosotros" class="py-20 bg-white"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center"><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px) translateZ(0)"><span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full mb-4">Sobre Climaya</span><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6">Tu empresa de confianza en Mallorca</h2><p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6"><strong>Climaya</strong> es la marca de <strong>Manteniments Costa Nord S.L.</strong>, empresa instaladora autorizada especializada en aire acondicionado en Mallorca. Con más de 15 años de experiencia, hemos ayudado a miles de familias y empresas a disfrutar del confort ideal en sus hogares y negocios.</p><p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">Nos diferenciamos por ofrecer <strong>presupuestos cerrados online</strong>, transparencia total y un servicio técnico certificado. Trabajamos con las mejores marcas del mercado para garantizar calidad y durabilidad.</p><div class="space-y-3"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Presupuestos cerrados, sin sorpresas</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Equipo técnico certificado y autorizado</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Equipos de primeras marcas con garantía oficial</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg><span class="text-gray-700">Servicio postventa y mantenimiento</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-3">